Joe Jonas (L) and Sophie Turner attend the 2019 Vanity Fair Oscar Party hosted by Radhika Jones at Wallis Annenberg Center for the Performing Arts on February 24, 2019. JOHANNESBURG - Joe Jonas and Sophie Turner tied the knot in a Las Vegas chapel on Wednesday night following the Billboard Music Awards. An Instagram live video shared by Diplo shows Turner walking down the aisle while dressed in a white jumpsuit, an Elvis impersonator officiated the wedding. WATCH: Priyanka Chopra stuns in wedding dress Entertainment Tonight reports that the couple, who got engaged in 2017, obtained their marriage license on the 1 May. Guests at the impromptu wedding service included Priyanka Chopra, Khalid and brothers Nick and Kevin Jonas.